Class NewInstanceDialog

java.lang.Object
  Dialog
      org.hfoss.posit.NewInstanceDialog

public class NewInstanceDialog
extends Dialog

Class specifically designed for adding newInstances and be called from anywhere in the application. The values are put into this from the NewFind like lat, long, weather and it adds the Name, description data to them and save to the instances database.
